document_data.name: Cypress
document_data.mainbody: '''Cypress''' was a type of tree that grew in [[Faer√ªn]].
document_data.Varieties: '''Black cypress''' could be found in the [[Shadow Swamp]], the reflection of the Vast Swamp on the [[Plane of Shadow]].
document_data.Habitats:
* Cypress was known to grow in the [[Great Swamp of Rethild]].
* Cypress was known to grow in the [[Lizard Marsh]].
* A grove of cypress trees was known to be in [[Anauroch]].
* In the [[Shining South]] one could find cypress trees in the [[Akhlaur Swamp]], the [[Kethid|Great Swamp of Kethid]], the [[Long Forest]], and the [[Wood of Dark Trees]].
* Cypress was known to grow in the [[Vast Swamp]].
